      "note_no": "26",
      "note": "This is a reference to 22:39-40. For an explanation of the expression muhkamah (\"clear in and by itself), see note 5 on 3:7. (As in the preceding sentence, the term surah has been rendered here, exceptionally, as \"revelation\".)"
    }
